312
00:19:00,576 --> 00:19:01,266
Got it?

313
00:19:01,290 --> 00:19:03,694
The Team Game will be more difficult for us.

314
00:19:04,535 --> 00:19:06,646
Miracle is good at the tactic "One Defended by Four".

315
00:19:06,971 --> 00:19:10,328
Its achievements over the years depend on its perfect defense.

316
00:19:11,185 --> 00:19:13,423
