319
00:19:19,771 --> 00:19:22,493
Kill their captain at all costs.

320
00:19:22,794 --> 00:19:23,714
I agree with it.

321
00:19:24,460 --> 00:19:26,864
But it would be hard to do without a Cleric.

322
00:19:27,404 --> 00:19:28,753
We must fight steadily in Team Game.

323
00:19:29,284 --> 00:19:30,212
No Cleric.

324
00:19:32,021 --> 00:19:32,600
What...

325
