329
00:19:44,736 --> 00:19:46,140
I'm not propagating for the opponent,

330
00:19:46,164 --> 00:19:47,648
but in terms of team strength,

331
00:19:48,044 --> 00:19:49,686
we still lag far behind Miracle.

332
