360
00:21:22,351 --> 00:21:23,581
But in the Team Game,

361
00:21:23,605 --> 00:21:25,517
because both teams have no Cleric on the field,

362
00:21:25,541 --> 00:21:28,509
the team that cooperates better will take control of the game.

363
00:21:28,921 --> 00:21:30,405
Back off. Don't let them get close.

364
00:21:30,603 --> 00:21:33,063
The longer the fight lasts, the better for us.

365
