522
00:32:34,001 --> 00:32:37,318
It means we have to concentrate on our training,

523
00:32:37,453 --> 00:32:39,524
and can't be distracted.

524
00:32:39,548 --> 00:32:40,508
It's boring here.

525
00:32:40,928 --> 00:32:42,341
Let's go back to training, OK?

526
00:32:48,420 --> 00:32:49,102
Captain.

527
00:32:49,887 --> 00:32:54,013
We have already understood your good intention, right?

528
00:32:58,998 --> 00:33:02,164
The cake vouchers given by Ye Qiu will expire tomorrow.

529
00:33:02,560 --> 00:33:05,060
They are free. Don't waste them. Take whatever you want.

530
00:33:06,012 --> 00:33:07,416
I want another one.

531
00:33:09,313 --> 00:33:10,154
However,

532
00:33:10,781 --> 00:33:13,654
who will pay the fare when we go back?

533
00:33:18,755 --> 00:33:21,762
Never mind. I want to stay here.

534
00:33:22,889 --> 00:33:24,665
Swearing everywhere on internet,

535
00:33:24,690 --> 00:33:26,722
Jia Shi's fans seem crazy these days.

536
00:33:29,673 --> 00:33:31,911
What were you talking about? Say it again.

537
00:33:31,935 --> 00:33:32,784
Stop it!

538
00:33:34,054 --> 00:33:35,736
OK, everybody,

539
00:33:35,950 --> 00:33:38,386
I'll show you something,

540
00:33:38,465 --> 00:33:40,131
These guys are from Xing Xin.

541
00:33:40,211 --> 00:33:42,179
Look at these ugly faces.

542
00:33:42,203 --> 00:33:43,472
What? Don't touch me!

543
00:33:43,695 --> 00:33:45,964
Come on, talk, talk to the camera.

544
00:33:47,710 --> 00:33:49,694
- Excuse me, stop shooting. - Leave me alone.

545
00:33:49,970 --> 00:33:51,104
You're the vice-captain.

546
00:33:51,319 --> 00:33:53,057
Don't let your guys bully us here.

547
00:33:56,181 --> 00:33:58,927
Come on, talk to the camera what you just said.

548
00:33:59,442 --> 00:34:02,045
- Dude... - Come on, cut the crap

549
00:34:02,307 --> 00:34:03,449
You just said...

550
00:34:03,680 --> 00:34:06,608
Jia Shi's fans seem crazy.

551
00:34:08,545 --> 00:34:14,219
Our captain we used to support is fighting for another team now.

552
00:34:14,243 --> 00:34:16,536
He's fighting desperately against his former team.

553
00:34:17,147 --> 00:34:19,607
Do you understand how Jia Shi's fans are feeling?

554
00:34:20,091 --> 00:34:20,829
No.

555
00:34:29,185 --> 00:34:30,907
You don't care about Jia Shi's fans, do you?

556
00:34:34,248 --> 00:34:36,914
My game is not played for fans.

557
00:34:37,684 --> 00:34:39,263
Then for whom?

558
00:34:40,477 --> 00:34:41,238
Frankly,

559
00:34:42,397 --> 00:34:43,666
we are just fighting for...

560
00:34:44,603 --> 00:34:46,190
our personal ideals.

561
00:34:46,737 --> 00:34:49,522
Nobody would fight for pleasing others.

562
00:34:50,205 --> 00:34:52,292
So, don't get it wrong.

563
00:34:52,736 --> 00:34:55,927
We're moved by, and appreciate your support and encouragement.

564
00:34:56,950 --> 00:34:57,584
But...

565
00:34:58,378 --> 00:34:59,814
I have to tell you,

566
00:35:00,997 --> 00:35:03,433
it's not true that we're playing for fans.

567
00:35:04,687 --> 00:35:05,933
At least...

568
00:35:07,329 --> 00:35:08,241
I'm not.

569
00:35:11,065 --> 00:35:13,065
But, without our support,

570
00:35:13,445 --> 00:35:16,762
there would be no pro games, and of course no pro players either,

571
00:35:17,937 --> 00:35:18,786
You're right.

572
00:35:20,484 --> 00:35:21,714
That's why I appreciate it.

573
00:35:22,198 --> 00:35:23,642
I'm also moved by your support,

574
00:35:24,777 --> 00:35:26,015
sincerely.

575
00:35:26,816 --> 00:35:27,950
But my game...

576
00:35:29,744 --> 00:35:31,238
is not played for fans.

